单，那么到底高端在哪里呢？ 镜像问题：有哪些看起来很暴力很初级的技术其实原理很高端？ - 科技"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-6e6b0f6f9f0f65ba51c66b31eecce757_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "94 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/33634376"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I1pH4gojp8+1GEAMaBzU2NjAzNDQg4OPmrQUwADiexgVAEnIIMzM2MzQzNzZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1776998445.421345", "card_id": "Q_2030281527729373348", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果有机会和 70 年前的中国航天人对话，你会如何向他们讲述今天中国航天的模样？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "今年是中国航天事业创建 70 周年。 70 年前，我国首个导弹、火箭研究机构——国防部第五研究院 (现中国航天科技集团、中国航天科工集团前身) 正式成立，标志着中国航天事业正式创建。70 年来，中国航天给你留下了怎样的印象？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-5368fd0ada619d3677551c872ce31bfe_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "88 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2030281527729373348"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI1pH4gojp8+1GEAMaCTExOTIzNzc2NCDlwaHPBjAAOCxAE3ITMjAzMDI4MTUyNzcyOTM3MzM0OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1776998445.422430", "card_id": "Q_655532760", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 34}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么现在铺木地板的人越来越少？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-20d87fc94165e0b148ec6fbfb68241f5_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "82 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/655532760"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I1pH4gojp8+1GEAMaCTEwNzk1MTU5OCCct/WxBjAAOFBAFHIJNjU1NTMyNzYweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1776998445.423340", "card_id": "Q_2030003275651625446", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 20}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "让你来设计杀戮尖塔 2 门扉 boss，其机制难度应如何调整？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "塔 2 发布新补丁后，3 天多了 1.5w 差评，很多玩家狂喷门扉的机制改动。 修改前最没存在感的 boss，一改被骂惨了。那如果你是开发者，你觉得怎么改合适？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-ca9eea7672348738244cd978a19c6371_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "81 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2030003275651625446"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI1pH4gojp8+1GEAMaCTExOTIyODY2MSDAu53PBjAAOA9AFXITMjAzMDAwMzI3NTY1MTYyNTQ0NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1776998445.424058", "card_id": "Q_29868843", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 382}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些数学定理或者数学知识惊呆了你？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "高考结束后，由于我有一本数学词典，我在上面看到了素数定理，由于素数是离散的，而素数定理的表达式是连续的（x/log（x）与素数个数函数 pi（x）的极限居然是 1），离散背后居然与连续扯上了关系。真是不可思议！ 还有就是黎曼假设，居然所有的非平凡零点都位于 0.5 这条线上，同样让我震惊！ 还有 miller rabin 素数判定算法，既简单又有效，很让我惊叹人类的智慧。 大家是否有类似的体会呢？说说具体例子吧"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-b2e7ca49734e83aaf28842f57b747433_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "74 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"},